  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dca \u0db7\u0dcf\u0dab\u0dca\u0da9 \u0d9a\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0d9a\u0dd1 \u0db4\u0dc3\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dcf\u0d9c\u0dda \u0d9a\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0dba \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The gang of five who robbed the gold items was arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Kesbewa police said that the gang of five who entered the house of a millionaire businessman in Piliyandala Halpita and robbed nearly 25 lakh rupees worth of gold items by putting pointed knives to his neck and threatening to kill him.",
        "The police say that among those arrested is a former army soldier and a drug addict in Miriswatte.",
        "The police have recovered the looted gold necklace earrings and bracelets.",
        "The police say that among the arrested people are people who spied and sold gold.",
        "The police say that the suspects who had entered the businessman's house on the night of the 16th of last month put a sharp knife on the neck of the businessman's wife and daughter and threatened to kill them.",
        "A police officer said that the businessman, who was scared due to the fact that the robbers said that he would kill Koloth, when leaving the house, complained to the police about the robbery on the 6th of this month.",
        "According to the police, the stolen gold items were pawned in Aluthgama and Maharagama areas and found based on the statements of the suspects.",
        "All the arrested suspects are drug addicts."
      ],
